textfsm_template:
Value HA_STATE (\S+)
Value HA_MODE (.+)
Value HA_PEER_IP (\S+)
Value HA_PEER_STATE (\S+)
Value HA_CONFIG_SYNC (\S+)
Value HA_HEARTBEAT_STATUS (\S+)

Start
  ^\s*HA State:\s+${HA_STATE}\s*$$
  ^\s*HA Mode:\s+${HA_MODE}\s*$$
  ^\s*HA Peer IP:\s+${HA_PEER_IP}\s*$$
  ^\s*HA Peer State:\s+${HA_PEER_STATE}\s*$$
  ^\s*HA Config Sync:\s+${HA_CONFIG_SYNC}\s*$$
  ^\s*HA Heartbeat Status:\s+${HA_HEARTBEAT_STATUS}\s*$$ -> Record
